  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632720/extras/b8259e3fd76896eeaf7d9be923c0c371.poster.avif?t=1750439814\" width=600 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632720/extras/b8259e3fd76896eeaf7d9be923c0c371.webm?t=1750439814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632720/extras/b8259e3fd76896eeaf7d9be923c0c371.mp4?t=1750439814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Brought to tryout by an EVIL mascot shark...</strong></h2><br>Play against Greg White Shark in a battle for your life as he tries to recruit you for his failing football team.<br><br><u><strong><i>Use your football against targets...</i></strong></u><br>Greg is putting you through several trials to see if you would make a good fit on his roster.<br><br><strong><i><u>Throw the anchor to stop foes...</u></i></strong><br>Once used as a prop for entertainment, now utilized to stop an enemy right in it's tracks.<br><br><strong><i><u>Collect serum to gain a speed boost...</u></i></strong><br>Dropped by your adversaries is a potion that gives you an advantage in combat and stealth.<br><br><strong>Make your way to the depths of the stadium and find the clues to get your way out!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632720/extras/b8259e3fd76896eeaf7d9be923c0c371.poster.avif?t=1750439814\" width=600 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632720/extras/b8259e3fd76896eeaf7d9be923c0c371.webm?t=1750439814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632720/extras/b8259e3fd76896eeaf7d9be923c0c371.mp4?t=1750439814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Brought to tryout by an EVIL mascot shark...</strong></h2><br>Play against Greg White Shark in a battle for your life as he tries to recruit you for his failing football team.<br><br><u><strong><i>Use your football against targets...</i></strong></u><br>Greg is putting you through several trials to see if you would make a good fit on his roster.<br><br><strong><i><u>Throw the anchor to stop foes...</u></i></strong><br>Once used as a prop for entertainment, now utilized to stop an enemy right in it's tracks.<br><br><strong><i><u>Collect serum to gain a speed boost...</u></i></strong><br>Dropped by your adversaries is a potion that gives you an advantage in combat and stealth.<br><br><strong>Make your way to the depths of the stadium and find the clues to get your way out!</strong>",
